text: Awaknyan teuma laen jipeugah Di jih jipeugah na aneuk Tuhan Padahai Tuhan suci that leupah Maha suci that kaya Neuh pih that Peue nyang di langet dum milek Allah Peue nyang di bumoe pih milek Tuhan Hana alasan peue nyang tapeugah Pakon tapeugah hana meupeue-peue Nyang han tateupue takheun keu Allah
